/dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-14-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-14-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-14-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-14-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-14-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-647x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-18-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Darimo proved a popular choice at this year’s champs, with Hall opting for a Darimo seapost. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_chris_hall_hill_climb_national_2023-15-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Almost a full house with Schmolke carbon saddle, stem and handlebars.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/cervelo_